{"tid":1762794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山中學校長避談何人決定報警","createTime":"2019-11-29T23:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T01:07:55.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ed41d30146905201d662e62c89778655f5e67a71","tid":1762794,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T23:56:05.000Z","msg":"】明愛馬鞍山中學有教師發現學生藏有不明化學品，校方通報消防及警方，又決定停課，警方則以涉嫌管有炸藥拘捕兩名學生。大批網民斥責該校一名教師涉嫌「篤灰」，哄騙兩名同學說出事件而被捕，質疑其做法不道德。該校校長蔡子良（圖）在網上發表千字文解釋學校停課的決定，卻避談是誰人決定，卻避談是誰人決定報警，未有回應外界質疑。<br />\n<br />\n教師被指扮黃絲篤灰<br />\n<br />\n蔡子良在校網上刊登一篇名為「重視每一個孩子」的校長的話，蔡稱自己與團隊決定停課，是作了一個艱難決定；文章亦提到，蔡子良與兩名涉事同學家長聯絡後，在他們知情下聯繫了警方的學校聯絡主任，警方於是派員到場檢驗，證實是危險品。不過，文章沒有解釋或澄清有關該校教師被指涉嫌「扮黃絲」及「篤灰」令兩學生被捕的指控，校長亦沒有提及是誰人決定報警。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》曾經向明愛馬鞍山中學查詢事件，職員回覆指校長蔡子良表示若傳媒查詢事件可參考學校聲明，記者再表示希望向校長詳細查詢，但校方至截稿前未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191130/OFPDDWLBU7HJSVXJ3SGIPY3HHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191130%2FOFPDDWLBU7HJSVXJ3SGIPY3HHQ%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=6ea960fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191130%2FOFPDDWLBU7HJSVXJ3SGIPY3HHQ%2F&h=e60cc6bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191130/OFPDDWLBU7HJSVXJ3SGIPY3HHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n仆街學校，送自己學生去死"},{"pid":"9a60064cc12907aa5e97124aeb8b0df2c0dfe6de","tid":1762794,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T23:59:04.000Z","msg":"報得警， 老師同校長應該商量過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"bdf221471886aae4e3bb07b7d5c045bb9f06e005","tid":1762794,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:01:36.000Z","msg":"明愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021e84b2d7a253e6f3f5a57901eff8e235e0fd8c","tid":1762794,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三育做過我班主任"},{"pid":"4292b52835e96e5ac886b536160294b4f0f67376","tid":1762794,"uid":31076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:30:26.000Z","msg":"有汽油彈一定要報警嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n否則自己處理一旦出事<br />\n<br />\n會係校長自己孭"},{"pid":"d0de9c19284903c6200a09f762d821181b54ce6f","tid":1762794,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蔡子良在校網上刊登一篇名為「重視每一個孩子」的校長的話，蔡稱自己與團隊決定停課，是作了一個艱難決定。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連登仔在連登上刊登一篇名為「重視每一個手足」的手足的話，手足稱自己與團隊決定裝修，是作了一個艱難決定。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"101175771a698e1e40e7ac57449e1605b8521dbe","tid":1762794,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4292b52835e96e5ac886b536160294b4f0f67376","tid":1762794,"uid":31076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:30:26.000Z","msg":"有汽油彈一定要報警嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n否則自己處理一旦出事<br />\n<br />\n會係校長自己孭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:55:55.000Z","msg":"俾我叫佢父母自己處理"},{"pid":"96fc3ec2572b5156086b7efda562b0d4b073d117","tid":1762794,"uid":214635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:56:09.000Z","msg":"唔係起左係個男老師報狗？"},{"pid":"2bff1eba4b927c1e93df43bd22414552045fbe98","tid":1762794,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"101175771a698e1e40e7ac57449e1605b8521dbe","tid":1762794,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4292b52835e96e5ac886b536160294b4f0f67376","tid":1762794,"uid":31076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited